user.biography: Chief Brand Officer @WWE, occasional TV villain, philanthropist, public speaker, and fitness enthusiast. Married to @tripleh & mom of 3 daughters.

node.text: @wwe is proud to partner on @adcouncil & COVID Collaborative’s “It’s Up To You” initiative, getting Americans important information about #COVID19 vaccines. The last year we’ve missed so many incredible moments, I can’t wait to have our fans back in person at #WrestleMania!

node.title: WWE & Ad Council “Back in the Game”

node.text: #TBT Connor’s Cure was created in honor of an 8-year-old @wwe fan who lost his life to brain cancer, Connor Michalek. #ConnorsCure has now raised over $3.5M in the fight against pediatric cancer in partnership with @thevfoundation. I will never forget the night I met Connor and fell in love with his shining light. I want to make sure, every year, we remind everyone of the boy who inspired it all.

node.text:
“Throughout this past year our @WWE Superstars performed tirelessly for all of you. Week after week, month after month, but we all knew there was something missing, something very important, THE most important, and that would be all of you - our fans the #WWEUniverse. And as we emerge from this dreadful pandemic on behalf of our entire #WWE family we would simply like to say 'thank you' and welcome you to, #WrestleMania!” -Vince McMahon
Then. Now. Forever. Together.
